_status\ncreated_at\n\n8. Figma Design Specification\n\nThis defines the UI layout that the Figma MCP integration will provide.\n\nHomepage Layout\n\nSections:\n\nNavbar\nSearch Bar\nCategory Sidebar\nFeatured Banner\nProduct Grid\nFooter\n\nLayout Structure\n---------------------------------\n| Logo | Search | Cart | Profile |\n---------------------------------\n| Category Menu                 |\n---------------------------------\n| Featured Banner               |\n---------------------------------\n| Product Grid                  |\n---------------------------------\n| Footer                        |\n---------------------------------\nProduct Card Component\n\nEach product card contains:\n\nProduct image\nProduct title\nPrice\nRating\nAdd to cart button\n\nLayout\n+------------------+\n| Product Image    |\n|                  |\n+------------------+\n| Product Title    |\n| $Price           |\n| ⭐ Rating        |\n| Add to Cart      |\n+------------------+\nProduct Detail Page\n\nSections:\n\nImage gallery\nProduct title\nPrice\nRating\nDescription\nAdd to cart\nBuy now\nReviews\n\nLayout\n---------------------------------\n| Images | Product Title        |\n|        | Price                |\n|        | Rating               |\n|        | Add to Cart          |\n---------------------------------\n| Product Description           |\n---------------------------------\n| Reviews                       |\n---------------------------------\nCart Page\n--------------------------------\n| Product | Qty | Price | Remove|\n--------------------------------\n| Order Summary                |\n| Total Price                  |\n| Checkout Button              |\n--------------------------------\nSeller Dashboard Layout\n\nSections:\n\nProduct list\nAdd product\nEdit product\nSales analytics\nOrder management\n\nDesign System\nColors\n\nUse the same couls as the mastercard colour paterns from graphit componennt.\n\nFonts\n\nPrimary Font: Inter\n\nHeadings: Bold\nBody Text: Regular\